name: PINEAPPLE MIVVI lolly
description:
Retro styled ice creams from popular ice cream van advertisements, They provide a great feel of nostalgia and would brighten up any wall.

This are CMYK hand screen printed, each are on Ivory Card Hammered 255gsm and are signed and numbered of 20. They are 210mm x 297mm in size..

£10 plus £1.50 P&P (unframed).. free postage on more than one print
